# Elite Writer v5 — Cursor Agent Rules

## CRITICAL: This is the CANONICAL Elite Writer repo
- The old `elite-writer-app` repo is ARCHIVED. Do not reference or deploy to it.
- Live URL: elitewriter.insightprofit.live (Oracle VPS)

## Never Delete
- client/ directory or any page components
- server/ directory or any routers
- drizzle/ schema or migrations
- shared/ types

## Always
- Work in feature branches
- Run `bun run build` before committing
- Preserve existing features when adding new ones
- Follow Drizzle ORM patterns for database operations
- Use existing Mantine/Radix/Tailwind component patterns

## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- Functional React components with hooks
- Express routers follow existing patterns in server/
- Database queries via Drizzle ORM (never raw SQL unless necessary)
